Clerics who take the Hatred domain tap the angst of dark hatred for power, and are granted spells to inspire fear and hatred in others.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Inspire Hatred: The cleric gains the ability inspire hatred towards the selected foe among his allies once per day.  The subject suffers a -2 penalty to their AC, Attack Bonus, and Saving Throws for 1 minute.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Scare (2), Rage (4), Blasphemy (7), Wail of the Banshee(9)</i>.